{"title":"Alarm Clock Online - Easy, Convenient and Free Alarm Clock","description":"Convenient, simple, accurate online alarm clock with sound and completely free. You can open it in full screen or select the alarm sound. Shows how much time is left before the alarm goes off.","content":"## Alarm clock online\r\n\r\nAn alarm clock is a device that beeps at a specific time.\r\n\r\nThe alarm clock allows you to precisely control the time by indicating a specific time. In the modern world, you no longer need to buy a separate alarm clock, now it is available in the browser itself!\r\n\r\nAlso, do not confuse an alarm clock with a timer! The alarm goes off at a specific, set time, whether it's midnight or early in the morning at 7:00.\r\n\r\n## Online Alarm Features\r\n\r\nThis alarm clock has many useful features that you will definitely need:\r\n\r\n* Multiple alarms can be set.\r\n* Allows you to set the time down to the second.\r\n* It is possible to change the background music and set your own music.\r\n* You can watch the remaining time before the alarm goes off.\r\n* The alarm start time is displayed.\r\n* The alarm will remain active EVEN after closing the browser tab.\r\n* The alarm clock is stored in memory, making it easy to reuse it.\r\n* Can work even without internet.\r\n\r\n## When can an alarm clock be useful?\r\n\r\nThere are situations for which an alarm clock is necessary at the right time:\r\n\r\n1. Control of working time.\r\nIt is worth setting an alarm and you will definitely remember the necessary break.\r\n2. During sports.\r\nYou do not need to control the training time, the alarm clock will do everything for you.\r\n3. When working at a computer.\r\nWhile at the computer, it is always worth taking small breaks.\r\n\r\n## How to use\r\n\r\nThis alarm clock is incredibly easy to use. You can take the time from the available list or choose your own. It's also a good idea to choose your own name for it if you plan to reuse it. You can select a unique sound for each individual alarm. After that, the alarm will be set.\r\n\r\nNow the alarm will go off at the time you set, you just have to wait.\r\n\r\nEach alarm can be stopped or resumed.\r\n\r\n## Arbitrary musical arrangement\r\n\r\nFor the alarm clock, it is possible to set your own musical arrangement for the operation of the alarm clock.\r\nTo do this, click on the `+` button next to the sound selection button. Next, upload the desired music, select it and apply the changes.\r\n\r\n## Historical facts\r\n\r\nThe first alarm clocks appeared more than 200 years ago and still serve the same purpose - to wake people up early in the morning. Over time, the approach to this process has changed: scientists have found and are finding more effective and pleasant ways to wake up a person. Conducted research on the influence of sounds and music, found clever ways to keep the awakened person from going back to bed.\r\n\r\nIn the modern world, some alarm clocks are even capable of forcing a person to solve problems until he wakes up. Or alarm clocks that appeared in Japan, which instead of sound send smells. Many believe that this is how a person wakes up better.\r\n\r\nProgress does not stand still and alarm clocks are already appearing that work depending on the sleep phase of a sleeping person, because it is known that it is easier to wake up during REM sleep, the shortest phase during which dreams appear."}